---
title: Steak and Mushroom Poutine with Garlic-Butter Snap Peas
description: Tonight, we're serving up an elevated spin on a Quebec classic: poutine with steak and mushrooms! Hearty roasted potatoes are topped with gooey cheese curds, DIY mushroom gravy and succulent pan-seared steak. Sugar snap peas tag along so that you can get your greens in!
